  <summary date="2022-02-10T20:47:15Z" status="Public Law">Ghost Army Congressional Gold Medal Act

This bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal to the 23rd Headquarters Special Troops and the 3133rd Signal Services Company, known collectively as the Ghost Army, in recognition of unique and highly distinguished service during World War II.</summary>
